{"type": "article", "id": 8215, "title": "Trio Love 婴儿车", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-08T07:57:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234534GySP7QbihxI03uOt.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t意大利儿童品牌 Chicco 邀请著名产品设计师 Stefano Giovannoni 为其设计了一款新型婴儿车。这款名为 “Trio Love”（三口之爱）的婴儿车旨在既给宝宝提供舒适和安全的环境，又满足父母们在实用功能上的需求，追求轻便、稳定性和方便性。设计师从运动学的角度入手，调整了手推车的重量和体积，车身采用铝制材料，精致而又牢固，配备有汽车标准的安全保险杠以保证安全性。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523453058KYPZQwzeJ0rv3n.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234531ZR63sWQegTcvjKSd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.87652812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234531oS8Cml2vMVET3ntK.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.07090465\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<em>可以折叠的婴儿车 Passeggino Chicco Love</em>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234531y35keu9YD1ig206n.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5620915\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234532TYJBk8ha3lEFcswq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.54054054\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><em>Navicella Chicco Love 提篮</em>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<em><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052345335fJPtBp9ygDAYhia.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.54054054\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</em>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<em><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234533EqHeP2D1BhtfKUIT.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5620915\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</em>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<em>Seggiolino Oasys 0+ 适合新生儿的小型提篮，可以稳固在汽车座位上。</em>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<em><br>\r\n</em>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}